{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"445b3493-3004-44f9-90fc-16fbcc4ec236","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n### 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\n`MSTest.Sdk` pulls in the MSTest runner, framework, and assertions automatically — no extra `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n### 2. Enable parallel execution (`.runsettings`)\n\nCreate a `my.runsettings` file (or add to an existing one):\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>          <!-- 0 = one worker per core -->\n      <Scope>MethodLevel</Scope>    <!-- parallelize across methods -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nThen reference it in your csproj:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\my.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 3. Run database tests sequentially\n\nUse `[DoNotParallelize]` on the class that must be serial:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanInsertRecord() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanReadBack() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n**How it works:**\n- All other test classes run in parallel across cores.\n- `[DoNotParallelize]` forces that class's methods to run on a **single thread**, and only **after** all parallel tests finish — so there's no concurrent DB access.\n\n**Key points:**\n| Concept | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| SDK-style simplicity | `MSTest.Sdk` — no manual package refs |\n| Parallel by default | `<Parallelize>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Sequential opt-out | `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute per class |\n| Worker count `0` | Matches logical processor count |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"aee99a69-040c-4841-b466-32c3bad9bbcb","outputTokens":574,"requestId":"BD11:3BF53A:1FA1CEA:23A7748:6A07CEF0"},"id":"fa153f4b-af8c-450f-ae35-7f537ede4c8a","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:57:17.132Z","parentId":"6e1b3ad2-9df6-44a8-8480-57b3716ec345"}
